</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:49
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='278000' id='t-278000'>So if you look at this, you might immediately grasp</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='280000' id='t-280000'>that different people have different numbers of connections.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='283000' id='t-283000'>Some people have one connection, some have two,</span>
