<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='322000' id='t-322000'>A. And you have an immediate appreciation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='325000' id='t-325000'>that A is going to be more likely</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='327000' id='t-327000'>to get the thing that's spreading and to get it sooner</span>
