<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='357000' id='t-357000'>So if you saw them contract a germ or a piece of information,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='360000' id='t-360000'>you would know that, soon enough,</span>
