<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='417000' id='t-417000'>The problem, however,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419000' id='t-419000'>is that mapping human social networks</span>
